---
import Section from '@/components/common/Section.astro';
import YoutubeEmbed from '@/components/common/YoutubeEmbed.astro';

import { type NavItem } from '@/constants/navItems';

interface Props {
	navItem: NavItem;
}

const { navItem } = Astro.props;
---

<Section
	id={navItem.label}
	title="What to Expect at Disneyland Resort">
	<p>
		Consisting of the original&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/destinations/disneyland/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Disneyland Park</a
		>&nbsp;and the adjacent&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/destinations/disney-california-adventure/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Disney California Adventure Park</a
		>, the sprawling Disneyland Resort is divided up into themed “lands”
		with related rides, shows, and attractions. Rising beyond Main
		Street,&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disneyland/sleeping-beauty-castle-walkthrough/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Sleeping Beauty Castle</a
		>&nbsp;is the unmistakable beacon at the heart of the theme park, with
		its turquoise-tiled towers, golden turrets, and working drawbridge.
		You’ll find an abode of an entirely different sort in the <a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disneyland/adventureland-treehouse/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Adventureland Treehouse</a
		>, which is inspired by Walt Disney’s <em>Swiss Family Robinson</em>.
		The treehouse is bigger and more impressive than ever after an extensive
		reimagining of the 1962 original.
	</p>
	<p>
		Visitors to the park in 2024 are in for a special experience to mark a
		milestone. Though the park opened in 1955, Walk Disney and his brother,
		Roy, launched the Disney Brothers Cartoon Studio in 1923. Beginning Jan.
		27 and throughout 2023, the park’s&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/100th-anniversary/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Disney100 Celebration</a
		>&nbsp;will mark the company’s centennial with special decor, food and
		drink, merchandise, and new rides and shows.<o:p></o:p>
	</p>
	<p>
		If you’d like to see all the goings-on and special events that will be
		taking place at Disneyland Resort in the coming year so you can plan
		your trip accordingly, see this&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2023/12/disneyland-resort-announces-event-dates-and-more-for-2024/?CMP=SOC-DPFY24Q1wo1130230004A"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>2024 calendar</a
		>.
	</p>
	<YoutubeEmbed
		videoId="gTDTiAjIv_E"
		playLabel="Play: Disneyland Resort Destination Promotional Video (2020)"
		title="Disneyland Resort Destination Promotional Video (2020)"
		class="mx-auto"
	/>
</Section>
